Text: i thought the same!! i was like “this is never going to work, i’m gonna swallow for sure” but nope! it was so much easier to control myself than i thought it would be

Author: TheAdjunctTavore
Text: Eyyy I c/s for the first time this last weekend. It was fascinating. I always thought it would take a lot of willpower but it was actually not bad. I had eaten until I was full but not stuffed and then decided to c/s the rest. Does that count as harm reduction??
